title: SAR operation to locate missing crew continues today (New Zealand Police)
text: ( Source : New Zealand Police ) Canterbury Police can confirm that five members of the Wellington-based NZ Police Dive Squad are helping with the recovery phase of the SAR operation to locate the F.V. Jubilee and the missing crew today.
